    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "I’m usually able to make any cat I see comfortable enough to come up to me for some love and scratches. I meet a happy little cat (named Luna) in the garden but she keeps her distance, rolling in the grass and scratching herself on sticks - no need for me. ",
            "link": null
          },
